{"tid":649284,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實係咪越窮越無料的人會越串？","createTime":"2018-05-01T12:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T11:32:43.000Z","uid":127610,"like":121,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"b79e09a56c08196474fede635f03bf01e3c8ba3a","tid":649284,"uid":127610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T12:05:18.000Z","msg":"純粹觀察所得，低學歷低收入的人<br />\n特別係d住公屋的廢老<br />\n會特別難同佢地相處，佢地有種心理防衛機制<br />\n由自痺表現得自大，串柒柒咁款<br />\n行路抬高哂個頭好有自信咁<br />\n咩都覺得自己啱哂，覺得政府欠咗佢咁<br />\n<br />\n相反，有少少錢的中產人仕<br />\n見識多d，知道個世界有幾大<br />\n會謙卑d，相處會容易d<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f640db8ddbcc21e5be7be144a8865de8a713260","tid":649284,"uid":100760,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T12:06:30.000Z","msg":"有自己一套性格就得 使乜跟個社會標準"},{"pid":"bec07410d12f9608a5544ac5242c4fbb610b0544","tid":649284,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T12:13:03.000Z","msg":"我啲下屬月入四萬左右，串唔串就一半一半啦"},{"pid":"536c538d0b9b0a1265a7716ac7ab9ab2f4b51040","tid":649284,"uid":45353,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T12:17:08.000Z","msg":"中產易相處？樓主未出過黎社會做野？"},{"pid":"636934d04e83e39dff327e075015efa7a8373e54","tid":649284,"uid":60321,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"536c538d0b9b0a1265a7716ac7ab9ab2f4b51040","tid":649284,"uid":45353,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T12:17:08.000Z","msg":"中產易相處？樓主未出過黎社會做野？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T13:19:37.000Z","msg":"感覺有少少唔同<br />\n中產都有人串 但個隻多數係見高拜見低踩 你有錢過佢勁過佢 佢可以死狗<br />\n但樓主個種人係咩都佢岩哂 佢講就道理 你講就歪理<br />\n當然 其實咩人都有 唔係全部都係咁"},{"pid":"a50923a75fb10d118a8cdf21ee6acedd8db14630","tid":649284,"uid":19955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T13:21:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a4cfe9b47e913dba5afc6c87330620032988f11","tid":649284,"uid":985,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T13:24